title: IAlarmStorageReaderConsumer (Interface)
text:
INTERFACE IAlarmStorageReaderConsumer EXTENDS __SYSTEM.IQueryInterface
This interface must be implemented by function blocks, that process the data read
by AlarmStorageReader.Read
